FT  14 MAY 94 / Auschwitz lie to be nailed
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
   By AP
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
   BONN
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
Leaders of Germany's governing coalition agreed yesterday to back
legislation making it a criminal act to claim publicly that the Nazis' mass
murder of Jews is a historical lie. Leaders of Chancellor Helmut Kohl's
conservative coalition said they expect passage of the law next Friday by
parliament's lower house, the Bundestag. Disseminating the so-called
'Auschwitz Lie' would be punishable on conviction by up to three years in
prison.
